{"tid":1684275,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「獨立調查」蘭桂芳慘劇 人踏人事件","createTime":"2019-10-31T04:16:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T08:17:12.000Z","uid":186,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5e303e257c1c121b6fdd33a8de08701c7f63fe57","tid":1684275,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:16:41.000Z","msg":"蘭桂坊慘劇是香港最嚴重的人群踩踏事故，1993年1月1日於中環蘭桂坊及德己立街發生，釀成21死63傷。事後<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港總督彭定康委任按察司包致金獨立調查事件</span></span></strong>，香港警務處在往後的大型節日慶祝地點均採取人群管制措施，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">地鐵則於同年12月起每年新年前夕提供通宵服務，避免慘劇再次發生。</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n事實證明<br />\n獨立調查後有咩用<br />\n點解今時今日又封鐵<br />\n又成班popo 水炮車Tg pepper<br />\n係唔係想人踏人再出現<br />\n港共政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ab090e8c647df90947047e11d6090f5d13d44567","tid":1684275,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:17:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/d2/Rthk-lck.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fd2%2FRthk-lck.JPG&h=362f2cf3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"568270ab0a897262fc181f360a20aad517ad2713","tid":1684275,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:17:27.000Z","msg":"你班popo 黨鐵 係唔係想死人啊"},{"pid":"9b10e94fb977e9f21f4c9b7d9d8b698f1f8a6124","tid":1684275,"uid":186,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:18:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>獨立調查完要你通宵行駛，避免人踏人<br />\n點解今時今日黨鐵係行相反，提早封鐵</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"55464142b631438f